'''南方過渡委員會'''（{{Lang-ar| المجلس الانتقالي الجنوبي|al-Majlis al-Intiqālī l-Janūbiyy}}）是[[葉門|葉門]]的[[分離主義|分離主義]]組織。委員會的成員包含南部5省的省長和政府閣員2人，由主張[[南葉門|南葉門]]脱离重新獨立的[[南方运动|南方运动]]派閥所组成。

2017年5月，南方過渡委員會宣稱已統治大部分葉門南部領土。<ref name="alaraby">{{cite web|url=https://www.alaraby.co.uk/english/news/2017/5/16/gcc-aden-based-southern-transitional-council-doomed-to-fail|author=The New Arab|publisher=alaraby.co.uk|title=GCC: Aden-based Southern Transitional Council 'doomed to fail'|accessdate=8 June 2017|archive-date=2018-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180719113829/https://www.alaraby.co.uk/english/news/2017/5/16/gcc-aden-based-southern-transitional-council-doomed-to-fail|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="alaraby2">{{cite web|url=https://www.alaraby.co.uk/english/News/2017/5/11/Governor-turned-president-Adens-Al-Zubaidi-announces-council-to-govern-South-Yemen|author=The New Arab|publisher=alaraby.co.uk|title=Banished Aden governor forms independent "South Yemen" council|accessdate=8 June 2017|archive-date=2018-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180719113959/https://www.alaraby.co.uk/english/News/2017/5/11/Governor-turned-president-Adens-Al-Zubaidi-announces-council-to-govern-South-Yemen|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="aawsat">{{cite web|url=https://english.aawsat.com/theaawsat/news-middle-east/thirty-southern-figures-reject-transitional-council-aden|author=Saudi Research & Marketing (uk) Ltd|publisher=english.aawsat.com|title=Thirty Southern Figures Reject Transitional Council in Aden – ASHARQ AL-AWSAT English|accessdate=8 June 2017|archive-date=2017-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171015234843/https://english.aawsat.com/theaawsat/news-middle-east/thirty-southern-figures-reject-transitional-council-aden|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title=Separatist group announces self-rule in southern Yemen |date=26 April 2020 |newspaper=[[Al_Jazeera|Al Jazeera]] |url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/04/separatists-announce-rule-southern-yemen-200426020425693.html |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200426074403/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/04/separatists-announce-rule-southern-yemen-200426020425693.html |archive